     main.main
        article.benefits
            h2.benefits__title Why choose Easybank?
            p.benefits__text We leverage Open Banking to turn your bank account into your financial hub. Control your finances like never before.

            .benefits__cards
                section.benefits-card.benefits-card--online
                    h3.benefits-card__title Online Banking
                    p.benefits-card__text Our modern web and mobile applications allow you to keep track of your finances wherever you are in the world.

                section.benefits-card.benefits-card--budgeting
                    h3.benefits-card__title Simple Budgeting
                    p.benefits-card__text See exactly where your money goes each month. Receive notifications when you’re close to hitting your limits.

                section.benefits-card.benefits-card--onboarding
                    h3.benefits-card__title Fast Onboarding
                    p.benefits-card__text We don’t do branches. Open your account in minutes online and start taking control of your finances right away.

                section.benefits-card.benefits-card--api
                    h3.benefits-card__title Open API
                    p.benefits-card__text Manage your savings, investments, pension, and much more from one account. Tracking your money has never been easier.


